And heiratour we charge zow yat ze tak alsa inquisitioun gif ony vnlawis or amersia- mentis war takin or rasit off ye said reuerende fathir or his predeces- souris for his or yair absens fra ye said ayris nochtwithstandinge yat it be wsit to cal yaim at ye said justice airis as' it is said. And gif it beis fundyne be ane guyd and leile inquisitioune yat γαί war nocht fawtit na nane unlawis rasit of yaim in tyme bigane for yar absence fra ye said justice airis, it is our wil yat yai be nocht fawtit na nane vnlawis rasit off yaim be zou in na tyme to cum for yar absence fra our said justice airis haldinge yir lettres for zour warrande. Gewyne undir our signet, at Fowlez ye xij day off Februar and off regnne ye xj zeir.
